commit.message: Update JWT pom to snapshot version
JWT release 1.0.1

Add JWT support for RSA public key PEM formats.

This makes it possible to create an RsaVerifier with
a PEM encoded public key. Previously it could only be
done with a private key or an ssh-keygen format public
key.
Tidy imports
SECOAUTH-366: don't clobber client_id by resetting authorizationParameters
SECOAUTH-366: add optional filter for token endpoint

Fix broken integration test

Recent changes to the sparklr sample mean that it is using a vanilla
basic auth entry point for the token endpoint.
Allow whitespace padding in private keys
SECOAUTH-388: apply ClientCredentialsTokenEndpointFilter only if not already authenticated
SECOAUTH-385: add null check for safety
SECOAUTH-385: fix broken URI query string parsing
[maven-release-plugin] prepare for next development iteration
Add javadocs for central release
[maven-release-plugin] prepare release 1.0.1.RELEASE
SECOAUTH-383: fix iterator logic for multi-valued parameters
SECOAUTH-142: make session peristed tokens optional
SECOAUTH-318: Add denyAll() catch all to token admin endpoints

SECOAUTH-361: Allow user to inject AuthenticationDetailsSource into <oauth:resource-server/>

Also fixed TestOAuth2ClientContextFilter test case
SECOAUTH-360: Add Basic prefix to auth errors from token endpoint
SECOAUTH-363: add old-style Pragma: no-cache to error responses
SECOAUTH-371: handle all client registration exceptions the same way
Add support for handling AccountStatus exceptions (expired, locked).
changed calculateCurrentUri to use ServleturiComponentsBuilder to keep parameters in order
SECOAUTH-372: use authentication key for comparison instead of complete authentication
Javadocs corrections
SECOAUTH-365: Fix ordering issue in current uri calculation

SECOAUTH-358: Provide support for Jackson 2

* add both jackson dependencies (2.0 is optional)
* add jackson2 dependency in bundlor template
* use both jackson 1 and 2 for OAuth2Exception
* use both jackson 1 and 2 for OAuth2AccessToken
* add specific jackson2 tests (with their own jackson2 objectMapper instance)
* fix @author tags
SECOAUTH-362: add toSTring() to auth details
SECOAUTH-359: check for missing grant type in TokenEndpoint
SECOAUTH-355: add serialization test
